==Translingual==

===Pronunciation===
/aa/ long open back unrounded vowel: as the a in [[father]] 

===Letter===
'''आ'''

# The second letter and vowel of the [[Devanagari]] script. It's [[matra]], used to modify the inherent vowel in a consonant is written &#2366;. For example the first consonant क with the matra looks like: का.

